     <int-org-section id="IO-UN.1214" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
          <heading>Organization</heading>
          <heading-note>April 2024</heading-note>
          <int-org-section id="IO-UN.1215" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
               <heading>UN-Habitat Assembly</heading>
               <p>The Assembly, comprising all UN member states, is the agency’s highest decision-making body. The inaugural Assembly session (UNHA1) was convened in May 2019, in Nairobi. The second Assembly (UNHA2) was initiated in June 2023, also in Nairobi; UNHA2 was to be resumed in May 2025.</p>
          </int-org-section>
          <int-org-section id="IO-UNHAB.1" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
               <heading>Committee of Permanent Representatives</heading>
               <p>Convenes every two years: once prior to the UN-Habitat Assembly, and a second time for a mid-term review between Assembly sessions.</p>
          </int-org-section>
          <int-org-section id="IO-UN.HABITAT.1" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
               <heading>Executive Board</heading>
               <p>The Board, which was inaugurated in May 2019, comprises representatives elected by the UN-Habitat Assembly from 34 member countries.</p>
          </int-org-section>
          <int-org-section id="IO-UN.1217" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
               <heading>Secretariat</heading>
               <p>The Secretariat implements resolutions of the Assembly and ensures the integration and co-ordination of technical co-operation, research and policy advice. It includes Offices of the Executive Director and Deputy Executive Director; a Project Office and Office of Management; an Office for External Relations that is divided into a Partners and Inter-Agency Coordination Branch and an Advocacy, Outreach and Communication Branch; and Branches of Urban Legislation, Land and Governance, Urban Planning and Design, Urban Economy, Urban Basic Services, Housing and Slum Upgrading, and Urban Research and Capacity Development.</p>
