               <p usage="ewyb">Regional offices deliver UN-Habitat work programmes at regional and country level. They are located in Nairobi (for Africa); Giza, Egypt (for the Arab States); Fukuoka, Japan (for Asia and the Pacific); and Rio de Janeiro, Brazil (for Latin America and the Caribbean).</p>
               <p>There are Liaison Offices in Brussels, Belgium, Geneva, Switzerland, and New York, USA; an Information Office in the People’s Republic of China; and a Project Coordination Office for Countries of the Commonwealth of Independent States, in Moscow, Russian Federation.</p>
               <p usage="edio">The establishment of a UN-Habitat office in Montréal, Canada, was approved in December 2022.</p>
